re used often with the ChilliCream GraphQL platform.</p>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">sdl</code> to describe GraphQL schemas.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"25889469535428880000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`type Author {\n  name: String!\n}`, `25889469535428880000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sdl\"><pre class=\"language-sdl\"><code class=\"language-sdl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Author</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> String<span class=\"token operator\">!</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">graphql</code> to describe GraphQL operations.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"94527391261393060000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`query {\n  author(id: 1) {\n    name\n  }\n}`, `94527391261393060000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\"><pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  author<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">json</code> for everything JSON related for example a GraphQL result.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"7471950380406156000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`{\n  &quot;data&quot;: {\n    &quot;author&quot;: {\n      &quot;name&quot;: &quot;ChilliCream&quot;\n    }\n  }\n}`, `7471950380406156000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"data\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"author\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ChilliCream\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">sql</code> for SQL queries.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"46846158299150600000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`SELECT id FROM Authors WHERE id = 1`, `46846158299150600000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> id <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> Authors <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">csharp</code> for C# code.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"21973042029590780000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied code example\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`public interface Author\n{\n    int Id { get; }\n\n    string Name { get; }\n}`, `21973042029590780000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Author</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token return-type class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span></span> Id <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token return-type class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">string</span></span> Name <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"use-images\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#use-images\" aria-label=\"use images permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Use Images</h1>\n<p>When using images make sure it's a PNG file which is at least 800 pixels wide.</p>\n<h1 id=\"use-tables\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#use-tables\" aria-label=\"use tables permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Use Tables</h1>\n<p>When using tables make sure you always use titles.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>ChilliCream</td>\n<td>A GraphQL platform</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/hotchocolate/hotchocolate/fetching-data/sorting/#headlines\">Headlines</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/hotchocolate/hotchocolate/fetching-data/sorting/#use-diagrams\">Use Diagrams